[
  {
    "text": "Hi, my name is Lauren Strehlow. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm a design evangelist, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=1"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we're going to be talking about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "designing for subscription success. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "Subscriptions are the fastest growing business model ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=7"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "But why is it almost every time ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're ready to sign up for some awesome new service, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "or subscribe to some new, exciting content, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=16"
  },
  {
    "text": "this is the feeling that you get? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "That’s because it's all too common ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "for subscriptions to feel complicated, confusing, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "and just take too long to sign up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=29"
  },
  {
    "text": "So for a great user experience, make your subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "effortless, transparent, and engaging. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "In other words, make it easy to subscribe.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's focus on each of these principles ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "to improve the user experience and design ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "for subscription success. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "What does it mean for your subscription to be effortless? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, it means people should know ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you have a subscription. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=59"
  },
  {
    "text": "They shouldn't have to look for how to sign up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "So be visible, get out there, and don’t be shy! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=63"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let people know that you have a subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "and ask them to sign up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "One approach would be to persist a subscribe button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "in you app’s interface. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "So here, in the New York Times app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "they persist -- tastefully -- a subscribe button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=80"
  },
  {
    "text": "that is visible across all of their articles, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "and this is done really well. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not annoying or pushy because it families together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=88"
  },
  {
    "text": "with their interface. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=91"
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't present your subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "like an a pop-up ad or notification, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "because ads and notifications are intended to be dismissed, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you don't want people to dismiss your subscription. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "Another way to be visible would be to present your subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=105"
  },
  {
    "text": "when a person has shown interest in a feature or piece of content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you offer through your subscription. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the dating app, HER, and as a category, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=116"
  },
  {
    "text": "dating apps have been in the subscription business ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a long time and they do it really well. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's just say you are swiping through a few profiles ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "and accidentally pass on someone who is cute, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "so at that moment you attempt to rewind. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, the app HER tastefully presents an option to subscribe, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=135"
  },
  {
    "text": "because the rewind feature is a part of their subscription. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=139"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's an appropriate time to present this offer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "because you've shown interest. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=146"
  },
  {
    "text": "And HER does a great job ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "presenting the values of their subscription offer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "right here with this beautiful, light animation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "So make it easy for people to sign up, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "make sure they know you have a subscription. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "Be visible, so you can choose to present your subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "when a person has expressed interest ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "or tastefully persist an option to subscribe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "But no matter which option you choose, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "all subscription apps should include a way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "to sign up from Settings or Account from within the app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "because that's an intuitive place where people would go ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "to look to sign up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, to make your subscription effortless, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "you need to remove friction. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "Friction is asking for too much effort ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "by asking for too much information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "and requiring too many steps to sign up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "But how do you know when you've asked for too much? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, this data should help. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "This graph represents a snapshot of one month of data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the top three entertainment video streaming apps in the U.S. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "While their names have been removed, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "the important data here is the clicks to conversion ratio. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "A subscription flow with three clicks ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "led to a 61 percent conversion rate, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=221"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a subscription flow with four clicks ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "led to a 48 percent conversion rate. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, nine clicks... ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=230"
  },
  {
    "text": "the conversation rate drops significantly to seven percent. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, while this is just a sample, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=236"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's clear that you should only ask ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "for what is absolutely necessary ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "because quite literally, less is more. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "Less clicks, less friction, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "will equal more conversion and more subscribers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "Focus people on singing up first. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=252"
  },
  {
    "text": "Personalization, favoriting, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "and requesting additional personal details ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "can all wait until after someone has signed up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "By being visible and removing friction, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=263"
  },
  {
    "text": "your app’s subscription will be effortless ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "and easier for people to subscribe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, let's talk about your subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "being transparent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "because transparency is the best policy, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you need to provide clear terms, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=279"
  },
  {
    "text": "so people understand what they are signing up for. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "Strive to be glanceable; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=284"
  },
  {
    "text": "in one view and in just a few seconds, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=286"
  },
  {
    "text": "people should be able to clearly understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "what your subscription offer is and how to sign up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "When making your subscription offer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "always include a concise value proposition, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "a strong call to action, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "a place to login for existing subscribers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "the ability to restore a purchase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=308"
  },
  {
    "text": "if someone has a new device, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a place to sign up that includes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "clear terms and pricing, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=315"
  },
  {
    "text": "and always offer multiple tiers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "because somebody may want to sign up for a day, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "a week, a month, or two years, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "so try offering three or four different subscription tiers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "to figure out what works best for your audience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "And be sure to follow App Review guidelines ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=331"
  },
  {
    "text": "to ensure that your subscription offer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "is within policy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=336"
  },
  {
    "text": "People have to have the ability to easily see ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "terms and conditions when they're asked to subscribe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "The MLB At Bat app does a great job ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=344"
  },
  {
    "text": "and offers all of this in one easy-to-understand, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=346"
  },
  {
    "text": "glanceable view. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "And all of this is important ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "because most of us are signing up on our phones. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=353"
  },
  {
    "text": "So please, keep it simple. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "By providing clear terms, people will be able to make ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "an informed decision to subscribe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=362"
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, I saved the best for last. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your app needs to be engaging from the start ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=368"
  },
  {
    "text": "before people subscribe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=371"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the best way to engage them is through experiencing your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "and all of its wonderful contents. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=377"
  },
  {
    "text": "Being able to experience and try before you buy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=379"
  },
  {
    "text": "is a part of how we all make purchase decisions today. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=382"
  },
  {
    "text": "From trying on clothes to attending an open house ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "or even test driving that car before you buy or lease it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "People are able to experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=395"
  },
  {
    "text": "before they have to make a purchase decision, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the same principle applies to your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are three ways to engage people through experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "and that will make it easier for them to subscribe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "First is a free trial, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "where people can try out the entire app for free, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=412"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a limited time. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "Free trials work best for established brands, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "when people already have an idea of what is included ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=420"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the subscription. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=422"
  },
  {
    "text": "So if you have an established brand, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=424"
  },
  {
    "text": "a free trial is a great way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "to let people engage with your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=427"
  },
  {
    "text": "and experience it before they subscribe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also make the majority of your app available for free ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=432"
  },
  {
    "text": "and offer a premium feature as a subscription. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, in the app Sleep Cycle, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can use most of the features for free, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=442"
  },
  {
    "text": "but the Trends feature -- shown here -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=444"
  },
  {
    "text": "is only available to people who have subscribed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sleep Cycle makes it really easy for people to sign up ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=451"
  },
  {
    "text": "right from here, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "and this is a great technique to offer people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "a peak of the content behind this blur, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=457"
  },
  {
    "text": "as it gives people an idea of the kind of data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=460"
  },
  {
    "text": "they would see as a subscriber. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "Third, sampling content is a great way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=466"
  },
  {
    "text": "to engage people through experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sampling helps people understand what type of content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=472"
  },
  {
    "text": "they would have access to as a subscriber, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=475"
  },
  {
    "text": "and this works well for a majority of apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=477"
  },
  {
    "text": "In the New York Times app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=480"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're able to read 10 articles free per month ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=482"
  },
  {
    "text": "as a non-subscriber. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=485"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a great sampling experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "because the New York Times lets people have control ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=488"
  },
  {
    "text": "over what they sample, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=492"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it allows people to find the content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "that they're interested in. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "In turn, that helps them better understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=497"
  },
  {
    "text": "the value of the overall subscription. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=499"
  },
  {
    "text": "The objective here is to let people experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "and become engaged with your app's content, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "and that content and that experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=508"
  },
  {
    "text": "will make it much easier for them to subscribe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "So no matter which option you choose, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=514"
  },
  {
    "text": "make sure it works for your audience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "Think about their current user experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=519"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the type of content that they currently have ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=521"
  },
  {
    "text": "available in your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=523"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how adding a subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "could impact that current experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=527"
  },
  {
    "text": "So design your subscription to be effortless ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=530"
  },
  {
    "text": "by being visible and reducing friction to sign up, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=532"
  },
  {
    "text": "be transparent with your terms and pricing, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=535"
  },
  {
    "text": "and engage people before they subscribe ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=538"
  },
  {
    "text": "through a rich experience of your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, it'll be easy to sign up.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-803/?time=544"
  }
]